*.pyc

# Rust
/target

# Self-host: reflow2's own graph is a RocksDB directory, and the agent MCP
# configs (.mcp.json, opencode.json, .vscode/mcp.json) carry absolute paths to a
# local build. All are per-machine, not shared state.
/.reflow2/
/.mcp.json
/opencode.json
/.vscode/mcp.json


# Trial records about real systems (storyflow, ophyd-service, personal projects)
# stay out of the public repo: they describe designs that are not reflow2's to
# publish. Kept locally; the public evidence base is the reflow2-self trials.
/docs/trials-private/
